    "mi_faq_page_healthier_skin_banner_m7bRLM": {
      "type": "mi-faq-page-healthier-skin-banner",
      "name": "t:sections.healthier-skin-banner.name",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Will the Qure Micro-Infusion System Work for Wrinkles?",
        "text": "<p>Absolutely! The Qure Micro-Infusion System is designed to be <strong>gentle and effective</strong> for most skin types, including sensitive skin.</p><p>We know that everyone's skin is unique, and that's why our device is crafted to minimize irritation while maximizing results. </p><p>The 24k gold plated micro-needles are <strong>designed to be virtually painless,</strong> and our serums are formulated to soothe and nourish even the most delicate skin.</p><p>So, if you have sensitive skin, you can confidently use our Micro-Infusion System to achieve a <strong>healthier, more radiant complexion.</strong></p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/micro_infusion-banner2.webp",
        "image_mobile": "shopify://shop_images/micro_infusion-banner2-M.webp"
      }
    },
    "mi_faq_page_healthier_skin_banner_CamYWx": {
      "type": "mi-faq-page-healthier-skin-banner",
      "name": "t:sections.healthier-skin-banner.name",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Will the Qure Micro-Infusion System Work for Dark Spots and Hyperpigmentation?",
        "text": "<p>Yes, it will! The Qure Micro-Infusion System is specifically designed to address a variety of  skin concerns, including dark spots and hyperpigmentation.</p><p>Our micro-needling process, combined with our rejuvenating serum, <strong>helps to penetrate deeply into the skin, reducing pigmentation</strong>and evening out skin tone. </p><p>The system delivers active ingredients directly to the areas where they are needed most, promoting a clearer, more radiant complexion.</p><p>With consistent use, you’ll notice a significant reduction in dark spots and a more even skin tone, helping you to reveal your <strong>natural glow.</strong></p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/micro_infusion-banner3.webp",
        "image_mobile": "shopify://shop_images/micro_infusion-banner3-M.webp"
      }
    },
    "mi_faq_page_healthier_skin_banner_HpGN7A": {
      "type": "mi-faq-page-healthier-skin-banner",
      "name": "t:sections.healthier-skin-banner.name",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "How Much Does the Qure Micro-Infusion System Cost?",
        "text": "<p>At Qure, we are dedicated to making advanced skincare solutions accessible and affordable for  everyone.</p><p>We’ve priced our Micro-Infusion System competitively because we understand that quality skincare shouldn’t break the bank.</p><p>Professional treatments can be costly and time-consuming, but with Qure, <strong>you can achieve similar results at home for a fraction of the cost.</strong></p><p>The Qure Micro-Infusion System, which includes the device and a 6-month supply of serums, typically retails at <strong>$713</strong>.</p><p>However, for a limited time, you can get it for <strong>just $219</strong> when you choose our best value bundle, <strong>saving you 70%</strong>.</p><p>We believe everyone deserves to look and feel their best without the high costs of professional treatments.</p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/micro_infusion-banner4.webp",
        "image_mobile": "shopify://shop_images/micro_infusion-banner4-M.webp"
      }
    },
