      "type": "mi-faq-page-text-with-image",
      "name": "t:sections.text-with-image.name",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Where Can I Purchase the Qure Micro-Infusion System?",
        "text": "<p>You can purchase the Qure Micro-Infusion System directly from our official website. This ensures you get the authentic product with the quality and results you expect.</p><p>Avoid imitations and knockoffs by buying only from our site. </p><p>We’ve designed our system to be effective and safe, and only our official website can guarantee you’re getting the real thing.</p><p><a href=\"https://qureskincare.com/pages/qure-microinfusion-offer\" title=\"https://qureskincare.com/pages/qure-microinfusion-offer\">Visit our website to order your Qure Micro-Infusion System today</a>.<br/><br/></p>",
